				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The shock line doesnt seem very reliable for spell interupts. Also the stun definatly has the draw back of agro and casting it at the beggining of any battle would certainly get you hurt, this spell would only really be usefull as a finisher. I like the 2 sec stun better than the 0sec interupt because for the last 18sec of the fight you would get an additional 33per slow to help finish the fight. Basicly a closing spell.
<br />
